                <text type="forecast">The chance of fog in the early morning. Mostly sunny day. Winds northeasterly 15 to 25 km/h turning north to northwesterly 20 to 30 km/h during the day. Overnight temperatures falling to between 9 and 12 with daytime temperatures reaching the mid 20s.</text>
