                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. Medium chance of showers in the morning. Winds northwest to southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h tending southeast to southwesterly 15 to 25 km/h during the morning then becoming southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h during the evening. Overnight temperatures falling to around 15 with daytime temperatures reaching the low 20s.</text>
